title: Kenny Dykstra
summary: Kenneth George Doane (born March 16, 1986) is an American retired professional wrestler signed to WWE as a trainer at the WWE Performance Center. During his past time in WWE, he was known as Kenny Dykstra and Kenny as a member of The Spirit Squad. Outside of WWE, his most significant appearance in a major promotion was for Major League Wrestling (MLW) in a tag team with Squad member Mike Mondo during 2019.
